flowchart LR
    AIN[Audio in ADAU1761] --> RX[i2s_ctl RX 24 bits]

    RX --> FIRL[fir left 24 bits]
    RX --> FIRR[fir right 24 bits]

    FIRL --> MIX[mixL mixR]
    FIRR --> MIX
    MIX --> TX[i2s_ctl TX 24 bits]
    TX --> AOUT[Audio out ADAU1761]

    POT[Pot 0 to 3.3V] --> DIV[Divider R1 24k R2 10k]
    DIV --> JXADC[JXADC XA_P0 XA_N0]
    JXADC --> XADC[xadc_pot_reader VAUX1]
    XADC --> PPOS[pot_pos 8 bits]

    SW[Switches mode and effect] --> FIRL
    SW --> FIRR
    PPOS --> FIRL
    PPOS --> FIRR

    CLK[CLK100MHz and pulse48kHz] --> RX
    CLK --> FIRL
    CLK --> FIRR
    CLK --> XADC
    CLK --> TX
